{"tid":2278531,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"請教貓貓隻眼有事","createTime":"2020-11-09T08:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T12:02:21.000Z","uid":99386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9c2984c9879a8ec6c3b8ded4b6679533aa6cb80e","tid":2278531,"uid":99386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:25:48.000Z","msg":"貓隻眼琴日朝早突然唔睜開<br />\n即日睇左獸醫，個醫生用咗啲嘢照咗<br />\n有事隻眼上面有片好似con咁既薄膜<br />\n個醫生話範圍都大 話係眼潰瘍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家滴左啲眼藥水同食左一日藥<br />\n仲係好似冇乜好轉 好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲打隻貓試過咁 有冇經驗分享下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47sXRh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47sXRh3.jpg&h=5d7fda32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89e0259bd57392de3d647bdb30f5484f0aa8e7cb","tid":2278531,"uid":126953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"至少一半療程先知嫁<br />\n唔放心嘅book定覆診 一完個療程再返嚟睇<br />\n利申：試過貓貓跑時撞傷之後眼潰瘍 滴晒就冇事"},{"pid":"d195b6098a470b1d8dbb8bb7bd044050f2a62f61","tid":2278531,"uid":99386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89e0259bd57392de3d647bdb30f5484f0aa8e7cb","tid":2278531,"uid":126953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"至少一半療程先知嫁<br />\n唔放心嘅book定覆診 一完個療程再返嚟睇<br />\n利申：試過貓貓跑時撞傷之後眼潰瘍 滴晒就冇事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:16:17.000Z","msg":"Book左覆診了 兩日後再去睇獸醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好擔心佢有事隻眼<br />\n唔該你"},{"pid":"6f3acfdf7f75381bb2f1c024d83faf177606ff97","tid":2278531,"uid":277072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"肉眼睇唔睇到個薄膜架？我隻貓依2日隻眼都半開咁。。"},{"pid":"dff16bed7c62ca7ff52d1bd8539bcf7284258e6b","tid":2278531,"uid":99386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f3acfdf7f75381bb2f1c024d83faf177606ff97","tid":2278531,"uid":277072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"reply